  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-75b3a070-0a48-49fe-a6fb-2158b7c733ba\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ab9e1fe1-9845-473b-9505-5963421ed753\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-11f2249c-2e3b-4dfe-848a-3403fb578189\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Story Boarding DAY 13</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c449aa6f-750e-4d7f-94e6-64925628718b\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d26aa5f5-b3fd-4223-ba37-c3b0a1011f4b\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4feddcfc-3b3b-41e4-a6dd-6c40b5533777\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7cc50d6f-b84f-4287-8d86-28fa5dd3512b\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>[요소정리]</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-388b7586-11fd-49de-9ddb-0efecbfb36f0\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1804c023-821f-4a76-9bdf-bab0cfe9b9d3\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>앞으로 7일간은 주문에 필요한 인쇄의 기본적인 요소를 정리하는 시간을 갖도록 하겠습니다. 27년의 인쇄 노하우를 가진 제가 좋은 자료를 만들기 위해 본격적으로 정리한 것이니 잘 읽어보시고 인쇄 주문이나 발주시 참고하셨으면 합니다. 인쇄발주시 가장 기본이 되는 디자인 부분부터 설명하겠습니다. 어제 올린 디자인 Part1의 추가 설명입니다. 시작합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-8a06b5f3-aab5-4d4f-ac73-5bc4c20c9778\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fdb476ef-5d8e-4cd1-aa0c-413d1678929e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-b4315437-920a-407f-b64b-30400484d7f5\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>디자인 요소 정리</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line5\" id=\"SE-33ac169d-2bc7-4e76-840a-48fb2c818010\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line5 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-717241c3-9d7f-4979-9d24-60a8a57ee5c9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-10c539cb-555c-4231-b4ae-ad82d6226660\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a96ab367-246e-4323-a36e-ce286748f2c6\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">사이즈</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-83b4e819-38ee-4b9e-aa77-40122d42a163\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-52af0f2e-b521-450f-90c0-dcf670ff1beb\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">텍스트 (서체) / 내용</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ff592f6a-785c-4306-9132-8d8a9a597dbe\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8a4d089e-dcfe-4aea-802d-2295abfbb6f2\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">이미지 / 사진 (포토)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7710ee58-918e-4f60-ab4d-f76eb429bc79\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-cedbc58c-be4c-4e34-b421-43cfaa7875f4\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">레이아웃 (폼, 형태, 효과 등)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0dd89cdf-d0eb-4fa4-8ada-4c868d11a3cc\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9da5973f-1825-44a0-beed-d81f48ca69d8\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">회사 참고 정보 (로고, 회사정보 등)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line5\" id=\"SE-32592b71-ab8f-4cc7-8165-5e881e89dcc0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line5 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-af47819a-eb1d-40f3-85ad-b7d566d65d61\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-96e5e816-c129-4b34-ab48-8fcb820f86bc\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c49e41ed-7b21-4b90-a5d0-7a8504e2e0ab\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">위의 자료를 토대로 디자이너가 \"</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c3cddf48-866e-4359-ab99-61baa922c69e\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>디자인을 한다</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-70220992-99aa-4120-9475-345ed6f8f666\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">\"라는것은 결국 다음을 잡기 위함입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-de1dd0fb-2805-46f2-9f5c-2e90642807be\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3f47c2b4-1086-4de6-92c6-bfb79e116573\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-6bc3866e-9af2-4b12-8921-970b8e07c153\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0ace6c2d-b9d7-4861-9215-b4b964f52eb1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-145e4e86-1bd3-4f44-8eec-a5689c51e59d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs28 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-db135737-c3f7-423f-9a45-2d772382d46e\" style=\"color:#0078cb;background-color:#ffffff;\">컨셉</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d1f19d58-5054-43f0-ac53-135e857d3063\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs28 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-de0a9328-540b-43b0-9a22-3357e48cb3ec\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-f1c16571-e4ca-47b8-acfc-1a12d423e398\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4d74d6a1-991c-4f48-a9d4-785968a720ce\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">디자이너는 고객이 보내주신 자료나 정보를 통해 고객의 니즈(Needs)를 파악하고 그것을 이미지화하여 일정 영역에 표현하는 작업을 말합니다. 이 결과물이 디자인이고 우리는 고객에 맞는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-856ef156-a958-4fe4-ac3b-1cee9ce8b72b\" style=\"color:#0078cb;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>컨셉</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-507ee91e-5839-43e1-b5b4-8d250595fc0c\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">을 잘 이해하고 표현할 수 있어야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8411883c-fdf0-47e6-a54b-059fcfced447\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-default\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-35cb6ee0-06a3-43d2-8c93-45ea76a29b8e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-4081ab3d-e5c6-4e99-9acf-2ca60f544b92\" style=\"\">좋은 디자이너란?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ee22e9ee-4ee7-40b0-b603-3fbf4fa69f3f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-82263cbe-1261-44c7-9765-bcfa40d53344\" style=\"\">고객이 보내준 정보나 자료의 니즈(Needs)를 잘 파악하여 표현할 수 있는 사람을 말합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-7217595a-9969-439b-801d-d1038bb8ac44\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-21ccc0bf-d570-4a96-af7a-3f84a3b5820b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-secti